OL,3,CKeir Starmer to chair first Cabinet
OL,4,Cmeeting since Wes Streeting's
OL,5,Cresignation
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer will assemble his new-
OL,8,Flook Cabinet for the first time on
OL,9,FTuesday after insisting again that he
OL,10,Fwould not "walk away" from Downing
OL,11,FStreet.
OL,13,FTuesday's regular Cabinet meeting will
OL,14,Fbe the first since Wes Streeting
OL,15,Fresigned as health secretary and
OL,16,Fcalled on the Prime Minister to quit
OL,17,Flast week.
OL,26,@rD@KOUrD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
